The user should be aware:

* leave entitlement accrues differently in a worker's first year - further information is
[available online](/holiday-entitlement-rights/calculate-leave-entitlement)
* when a worker leaves employment within the first 12 months, their leave is calculated using the 'For somebody
starting and leaving part way through a leave year' option in the calculator
* this entitlement may be subject to a statutory cap of 28 days per year
* this entitlement may need to be rounded up to the next half day of the worker's working pattern
